note.para:
Users who prefer to statically compile &man.atapicam.4;
	  support into the kernel, should add this line to the
	  kernel configuration file:

listitem.para:
Have a good understanding of
	    &os;
	      networking.

sect2.programlisting:
resource test {
	on hasta {
		local /dev/ad6
		remote 172.16.0.2
	}
	on hastb {
		local /dev/ad6
		remote 172.16.0.1
	}
}

sect3.programlisting:
notify 30 {
	match "system" "IFNET";
	match "subsystem" "carp0";
	match "type" "LINK_UP";
	action "/usr/local/sbin/carp-hast-switch master";
};

notify 30 {
	match "system" "IFNET";
	match "subsystem" "carp0";
	match "type" "LINK_DOWN";
	action "/usr/local/sbin/carp-hast-switch slave";
};
